text: Supermac's is an Irish fast food restaurant chain. It opened its first restaurant in Ballinasloe, County Galway in 1978. It has 118 restaurants in Ireland. Its head office is in the Ballybrit Business Park in Ballybrit, County Galway. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Fast-food restaurants Category:1970s establishments in Europe
